<p>If after 30 days, you are entitled to repair or replacement/ exchange if clothing.<br>
You must return the item within the <b>first 6 months</b>, it will be easier as you do not need to prove who has caused the fault.<br>
The seller must offer you a repair within a reasonable time frame, if they cannot do this, they must offer you a replacement. You should receive an exchange in clothing, however, please consult the stores policies.<br>
If neither can be offered, they can offer you a refund or a discounted price of the item, if you still wish to keep it.</p>